as/ecb7eac7a820998d5d1b44fda3750e2e.mp4?t=1709579508\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >NEW THIRD CHAPTER</h2>But that's not all! AVGN Deluxe also comes with a special new chapter, adding even more excitement to your Nerd experience. This chapter extends and caps off the story that now spans between both games.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1162960/extras/2fb2256fff2ba90f14922288674fe8b8.poster.avif?t=1709579508\" width=620 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1162960/extras/2fb2256fff2ba90f14922288674fe8b8.webm?t=1709579508\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1162960/extras/2fb2256fff2ba90f14922288674fe8b8.mp4?t=1709579508\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >IMPROVED GAMEPLAY AND CONTROLS</h2>With updated gameplay mechanics, improved controls, and carefully crafted level designs, you'll be put to the test as you strive to master each stage and defeat the challenges that await. Get ready to unleash your inner Nerd and embark on an action-packed adventure like never before. Are you up for the challenge? Grab your controller and get ready to rage!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1162960/extras/f4ba81b84cd4075d7eae9ed36e461a7d.poster.avif?t=1709579508\" width=620 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1162960/extras/f4ba81b84cd4075d7eae9ed36e461a7d.webm?t=1709579508\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1162960/extras/f4ba81b84cd4075d7eae9ed36e461a7d.mp4?t=1709579508\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>